releases.message:
This is an initial release of the IronSource SDK for Defold.
At the moment, the following functionality is lacking:
- it's [impossible to initialize the SDK separately for different AD Units](https://github.com/defold/extension-ironsource/issues/2);
- [no iOS support](https://github.com/defold/extension-ironsource/issues/6) (it supports only **Android**);
- no [Banners](https://github.com/defold/extension-ironsource/issues/3) or [Offerwalls](https://github.com/defold/extension-ironsource/issues/4) (only **Interstitial** ADS and **Rewarded** ADS);
- the following mediation adapters are not added: [APS](https://github.com/defold/extension-ironsource/issues/1), [Maio, Smaato, SuperAwesome](https://github.com/defold/extension-ironsource/issues/5).
